      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' colspan=2 class='db'><span class='dbti'>TO AWESOME TO BE TRUE</span><b>, By Jumangia</b> <small>(1/28/2001)</small><br><br>Ok all or most of you are disappointed. Me I would love to have one of these weapons. I'm low lvl but I don't care for the Proc or if it is made clickable. If you are in a well rounded group you shouldn't have to worry about it procing. I rely on the bard to lull and the druid to dot the tank to tank and the wiz and myself to blast. And about the cleric you have to Love them for they will always keep you alive so leave them out of this. I always reserve mana for when our cleric is getting low as to save someones Life if need be. I catch myself saying that others get the best weapons then some so please quit whinning and except what you can get and move on. If you really want to talk about crappy weapons then ask a ranger about weapons for duel wield that do crappy damage and soloing is out of the question completly. So quit gripping and be happy they are trying to get better weapons in the game for all classes.                  <br><hr size='1'></td>
